  "text": "Regards to the mechanism of BCRP, it was previously shown that PI3K inhibitors LY294002 and wortmannin induced internalization of BCRP [CITATION_1] . Another report showed that LY294002, but not wortmannin, reversed the BCRP-mediated SN-38 and topo-tecan resistance [CITATION_2] .",
